            <text>
                <body>
                    <div type="edition">
                        <div type="textpart">
                            <ab>Il <rs key="#Notary">notaio imperiale</rs>
                        <persName key="#Notary"><name ref="Gotefredus/Morectus">Gottifridi</name>
                            detto Moretto</persName> del <persName>fu <name ref="Podo"
                            >Boddo</name></persName> e la moglie <persName><name ref="Berta"
                                >Berta</name></persName> del <persName>fu <name ref="Ursus"
                                >Orso</name></persName>, con il consenso del marito, interrogata dal
                            <rs key="#Judge #Other_palatine_officer">giudice del sacro palazzo</rs>
                        <persName key="#Witness #Other_palatine_officer #Judge"><name ref="Iohannes"
                                >Giovanni</name></persName>, offrono pro anima loro al <rs
                            key="#Monasteries">monastero</rs> di <orgName
                            ref="#juridical_persons/71" key="#Landed_possessions #Monasteries">San
                            Ponziano</orgName> di <placeName ref="#places/4">Lucca</placeName>,
                        omnibus casis et terris seo rebus poste in loco et finibus <placeName
                            ref="#places/36">Saltochio</placeName> ubi dicitur <placeName
                            ref="#places/36">a la Piastre</placeName> et ubi dicitur <placeName
                            ref="#places/36">Vergelloro</placeName> et ubi dicitur <placeName
                            ref="#places/36">a Vimgna Vergelloro</placeName> et in eorum finibus,
                        con tutte le loro dipendenze. Chiedono al <rs key="#Notary #Writer">notaio
                            imperiale</rs>
                        <persName key="#Notary #Writer"><name ref="Rodulfus"
                            >Rodolfo</name></persName> la stesura della cartula. Actum foris Luca
                        prope suprascripta ecclesia et monasterio Sancti Pontiani. <rs
                            key="#Witness">Testimoni</rs> sottoscrittori: Giovanni iudex sacri
                        palatii, <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Wido">Guido</name></persName>,
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Wido">Guido</name></persName> del
                            <persName key="#Judge">fu <name ref="Rodelandus"
                            >Rodilando</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudex</rs>, <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Hubertus"
                                >Uberto</name></persName>.</ab>
                        </div>
                    </div>
